<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.253585>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Habitus images of living adult individuals of Thai phylines. A. Sejanus adustopaca, holotype male (Nakhon Nayok). B. D. anthophila, male (Nakhon Nayok). C. Ditto, female. D. D. taksini (Nakhon Nayok). E. Decomia indochinensis, male (Nakhon Nayok). F. Malaysiamiris nigrescens, male (SERS). G. Ditto, female. H. Tytthus chinensis, female (Nakhon Nayok). I. Lasiolabops cosmopolites, female (SERS). J. Sthenaridea rufescens, female (Chaiyaphum)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/253585/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.253590>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Male genitalia of three new phyline species from Thailand." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/253590/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

